                    ],
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "autoplay": true,
                            "type": "video",
                            "videoUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/text-based-editing/9b5d4c81-f432-44f8-ac10-effe5db5e716.mp4"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Assemble your rough cut using Text-Based Editing",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Learn about Text-Based Editing by watching the video above. Then, complete the steps below.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Open the Text panel by choosing <$Window$> > <$Text$> in the application menu."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "autoplay": true,
                            "type": "video",
                            "videoUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/text-based-editing/b8d44740-da3e-4289-a150-7d67970738d2.mp4"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Add clips using the transcription",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Try updating the speaker names and using the search function to locate the clips we want to use and add them to the timeline. To make things simpler, you'll focus on the clip Billy_Interview.mp4 in this step. Then in the next step, you'll practice what you've learned using the clip JD_Interview.mp4.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Double-click on Billy_Interview.mp4 in the <$Project$> panel to open it in the <$Source Monitor$>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "In the <$Text$> panel, click on Speaker 1 and choose <$Edit speaker name$> from the menu."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "In the <$Edit Speakers$> dialogue box, change <$Speaker$> 1 to Interviewer and <$Speaker 2$> to Billy."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "clipAdded",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Billy_Interview.mp4",
                                                "layerName": "Video 1"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "showOnComplete": {
                                        "heading": "Great Job!",
                                        "texts": [
                                            "You were successfully able to find the point in Billy's clip where he explained the premise of the movie Devotion and add it to the timeline. In the next section you'll practice this by adding a clip from J.D.'s interview to the timeline."
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "text": "In the search bar, enter the word \"devotion\" and find the dialogue that begins, \"Well, the story of devotion…\" Highlight the paragraph and select <$Insert$>."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "text": "Practice adding clips using the transcription",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Take a moment to practice what you learned in the last step using the clip JD_Interview.mp4. If you aren't sure what to do, you can go back and review the previous step, or you can use the hints provided below.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Update the speaker names by changing <$Speaker 1$> to Interviewer and <$Speaker 2$> to J.D.."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "clipAdded",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "JD_Interview.mp4",
                                                "layerName": "Video 1"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "Search the transcript for the word devotion and add the paragraph that begins, \"Devotion tells the story…\" to the timeline."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "isCtiOverClip",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Billy_Interview.mp4"
                                            }
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "check": "isCtiOverClip",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "JD_Interview.mp4"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "showOnComplete": {
                                        "heading": "Fantastic!",
                                        "texts": [
                                            "You were able to add a clip to the timeline using the transcript. In the next step, you'll learn how to refine your rough cut using text-based editing."
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "text": "Move the playhead to the beginning of the clip and press the <%{KEY.SPACEBAR}%> to play the sequence."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        },
                        {
                            "heading": "Hint 1",
                            "icon": "hint",
                            "texts": [
                                "What should you do to show the clip JD_Interview.mp4 in the source monitor? Which panel is the transcript visible in?"
                            ],
                            "type": "toggleable"
                        },
                        {
                            "heading": "Hint 2",
                            "icon": "hint",
                            "texts": [
                                "Double click on the clip in the <$Project$> panel, then use the <$Text$> panel to search for devotion and insert the clip."
                            ],
                            "type": "toggleable"
                        },
                        {
                            "heading": "Hint 3",
                            "icon": "hint",
                            "texts": [
                                "In the <$Project$> panel, double-click on the clip JD_Interview.mp4. Then, in the <$Text$> panel, search for devotion and highlight the paragraph that begins \"Devotion tells the story…\" Finally, click <$Insert$> to add it to the timeline."
                            ],
                            "type": "toggleable"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "autoplay": true,
                            "type": "video",
                            "videoUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/text-based-editing/1739e637-9fe2-4e3c-9d2b-c598cf3b20fa.mp4"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Rearrange and trim clips using the transcript",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Try moving J.D.'s clip to the beginning of the sequence and trimming Billy's clip.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "text": "In the Text panel, highlight J.D.'s dialogue and press <%{KEY.COMMAND_CONTROL.{{osName}}}%> + <%X%> to copy the text."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "clipMoved",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "JD_Interview.mp4"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "Move your cursor to the beginning of Billy's dialogue and press <%{KEY.COMMAND_CONTROL.{{osName}}}%> + <%V%>. J.D.'s clip will now be before Billy's clip in the timeline."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "clipLengthChanged",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Billy_Interview.mp4",
                                                "layerName": "Video 1"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "In the Text panel, select the beginning of Billy's dialogue leaving only the sentence starting with \"And devotion is about his devotion with aviation…\" Then, press <%{KEY.DELETE}%> to trim the clip."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "isCtiOverClip",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "JD_Interview.mp4"
                                            }
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "check": "isCtiOverClip",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Billy_Interview.mp4"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "showOnComplete": {
                                        "heading": "Awesome!",
                                        "texts": [
                                            "Now the sequence flows really nicely as an introduction to the behind-the-scenes interviews. When you're ready, click next to learn more about how you can edit clips using only the transcript."
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "text": "Move the playhead to the beginning of the timeline and press the <%{KEY.SPACEBAR}%> observe the changes."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "autoplay": true,
                            "type": "video",
                            "videoUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/text-based-editing/1cf6b47c-b02f-448f-a549-6f2cf75285e8.mp4"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Remove pauses using text-based editing",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Try to refine this edit further by deleting the pauses at the end of J.D.'s dialogue and the beginning of Billy's dialogue.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "clipLengthChanged",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "JD_Interview.mp4",
                                                "layerName": "Video 1"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "In the <$Text$> panel, select the ellipses at the end of J.D.'s dialogue and press <%{KEY.DELETE}%>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "clipLengthChanged",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Billy_Interview.mp4",
                                                "layerName": "Video 1"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "Select the ellipses at the beginning of Billy's dialogue and press <%{KEY.DELETE}%>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "isCtiOverClip",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "JD_Interview.mp4"
                                            }
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "check": "isCtiOverClip",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Billy_Interview.mp4"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "showOnComplete": {
                                        "heading": "Fantastic!",
                                        "texts": [
                                            "Great job creating this rough-cut using text based editing. Check out the tutorial \"Include captions to improve engagement\" to learn how to use your transcript to create captions."
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "text": "Press the <%{KEY.SPACEBAR}%> to watch the sequence to see how deleting the pauses changed it."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        },
                        {
                            "texts": [
                                "In Premiere Pro version 24.3, filler word detection was added, allowing you to quickly identify and delete words like \"umm\" and \"uh\". You can enable filler word detection by choosing the filter icon in the <$Text$> panel and selecting <$Filler words$>. If you do not have this option, make sure you have the most up-to-date version of Premiere Pro installed."
                            ],
                            "type": "well",
                            "wellType": "info"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "successHeading": "Congratulations!",
                            "successText": "You just learned how to use text-based editing to assemble a rough cut. Use this workflow in your own projects to assemble your rough cuts faster than ever!",
                            "type": "endScreen"
                        }
                    ]
                }
